        <mxCell id="fWWQNCZk1dSUgq2n23bQ-40" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Explanations&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;UGC will provide digital identities (wallets) to the Issuers, Companies, Candidates and other stakeholders of the platform.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;UGC will maintain the permissions and roles of the issued digital identities.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Users (Company, Candidate, Issuer) can access to the platform and blockchain network using their wallet credentials&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Blockchain gateway is an interface to access to the private blockchain network for UGC Server or any other authorized entity&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In Private Blockchain network, the records will be stored.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Private blockchain network can be utilized to build a consortium and consensus layer.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Using the chaincodes and smart contracts, the transactions will be validated for the record issuance (or any other) process.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Public blockchains can be utilized to create a cryptographical evidence of a record.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Data to Document converter can be developed to compose PDFs with a defined template for various type of documents.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For user conveniece, communication channels will be used to send email, sms etc.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="fWWQNCZk1dSUgq2n23bQ-1" vertex="1">
